TableContextTimeStampAfterTable: {351205=Continental have a comprensive range of bicycle tyres. Contental have bicycle tyres designed specifically for your off-road, road, city/touring and cyclocross bike. Continental has been developing and manufacturing bicycle tyres since 1892 in Hannover, Germany. Their modern-day bicycle tyres are technologically advanced products designed to care for different biking habits and different types of bicycles. Continental has ten different tread patterns in its MTB tyre range alone. Owners of touring bikes and racers can also choose from a wide spectrum of tyres. What’s more, for the modern harsh winters in northern europe, there’s also a studded winter tyre series for both trekking and mountain bikes.}
